reviewText: Very easy to follow very good material! 5 stars.

I started doing Butterfly guard years ago when it was first introduced to me at a Royler Gracie seminar.  Kesting breaks down the butterfly guard down better then Gracie did!
I was worried that the x-guard may be too complex for my game but the way that kesting breaks it down I was able to use it almost immediately.
Awesome product!  Thanks Stephan!
This was my tutorial for sweeping my opponents for a guard position. What my instructor didn't cover Stephan did. I recommend it to all.
